        <div>
            <div class="section">
                <p>
                    To download the sources you can go to the
                    <a href="http://sourceforge.net/project/showfiles.php?group_id=228491&package_id=276725" target="_blank">
                        project's download page
                    </a>
                    and choose the
                    <span class="filepath">
